    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1891-12-24T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1891-12-24T00:00:00-05:00" n="469" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d469">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Sir <persName type="from">Julian
                                    Pauncefote</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Blaine</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-12-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 24,
                                    1891</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor, in obedience to
                            instructions which I have received from the Marquis of Salisbury, to
                            transmit to you copy of an instruction which has been addressed to Her
                            Majesty’s consul at Apia, relative to the currency question, together
                            with copies of previous correspondence on the subject, as marked in the
                            margin.</p>
                <p>You will observe that Her Majesty’s consul has been instructed to act
                            with his German colleague in urging the Samoan Government to adopt the
                            arrangements proposed by the municipal council of Apia, on the 3d of
                            June and the 24th of July last, and Lord Salisbury has instructed me to
                            request you, should you see no objection, to issue orders to the U.S.
                            consular representative at Apia similar to those which have been sent to
                            Her Majesty’s consul.</p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Julian
                            Pauncefote.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
